snippet.title: WrestleQuest - Legends Trailer
snippet.description:
In WrestleQuest, your rise to stardom begins at the feet of Giants.... and the only way to earn a Legend’s respect... is victory! Check out how you’ll be interacting with wrestling’s greats in the game.
